---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHead from '../../components/PageHead.astro';
import { t } from '../../i18n';

const lang = 'en';
const lastUpdated = 'May 7, 2026';
---
<BaseLayout
  lang={lang}
  canonicalPath="/en/privacy/"
  altLangUrl="/ochrana-osobnych-udajov/"
  title="Privacy Policy — Filip Lopatka"
  description="Privacy policy and cookie use for lopatka.sk."
>
  <PageHead
    eyebrow={t('legal.privacy.nav', lang)}
    titleHtml="Privacy <em>policy</em>."
    lead={`${t('legal.lastUpdated', lang)}: ${lastUpdated}`}
  />

  <article class="legal">
    <section>
      <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
      <p>
        The controller of personal data processed via this website is
        <strong>Filip Lopatka</strong>, a self-employed individual operating under a
        Slovak business license (živnostenské oprávnenie).
      </p>
      <ul class="legal-meta">
        <li><span>Address:</span> <em class="placeholder">{`{{REGISTERED ADDRESS, POSTCODE CITY}}`}</em></li>
        <li><span>Business ID (IČO):</span> 56 881 738</li>
        <li><span>Tax ID (DIČ):</span> 1121341166</li>
        <li><span>E-mail:</span> <a href="mailto:filip@lopatka.sk">filip@lopatka.sk</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. What data I collect</h2>
      <p>I only process data you provide voluntarily through the contact or brief form:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Identification:</strong> first name, last name, optionally company name.</li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> e-mail address, optionally phone.</li>
        <li><strong>Message content:</strong> project description you submit through the form.</li>
        <li><strong>Server technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, access time — kept short-term in hosting access logs for security purposes.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Purpose and legal basis</h2>
      <p>
        I process your personal data solely to <strong>respond to your inquiry</strong>,
        prepare a quote, and potentially conclude an agreement to deliver web services.
      </p>
      <p>Legal bases under GDPR (Art. 6(1)):</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>(b)</strong> — pre-contractual measures and contract performance,</li>
        <li><strong>(f)</strong> — legitimate interest (web security via access logs).</li>
      </ul>
      <p>I do not run marketing, newsletters, or profiling. I never sell or transfer data outside the EU.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Retention period</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Form submissions:</strong> 3 years from last communication (Slovak Civil Code statute of limitations).</li>
        <li><strong>Accounting records (if a contract is concluded):</strong> 10 years (Act 431/2002 on Accounting).</li>
        <li><strong>Server access logs:</strong> 30 days.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Recipients of data</h2>
      <p>I do not share data with third parties except for the following processors providing technical services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Web hosting:</strong>
          <em class="placeholder">{`{{hosting provider — e.g. GitHub Pages, Microsoft, USA — or WebSupport, SK}}`}</em>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>E-mail server:</strong>
          <em class="placeholder">{`{{email provider — e.g. Google Workspace, Proton, self-hosted}}`}</em>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Contact form processor:</strong>
          <em class="placeholder">{`{{Formspree / Web3Forms / other — or "n/a, e-mailed directly"}}`}</em>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>I have GDPR-compliant Data Processing Agreements (DPA) with all of them.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
      <p>As a data subject, under GDPR (Art. 15–22) you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>access</strong> your data,</li>
        <li><strong>rectification</strong> of inaccurate data,</li>
        <li><strong>erasure</strong> ("right to be forgotten"),</li>
        <li><strong>restrict processing</strong>,</li>
        <li><strong>data portability</strong>,</li>
        <li><strong>object</strong> to processing,</li>
        <li><strong>file a complaint</strong> with the supervisory authority (Slovak Data Protection Office, <a href="https://dataprotection.gov.sk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">dataprotection.gov.sk</a>).</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, e-mail me at
        <a href="mailto:filip@lopatka.sk">filip@lopatka.sk</a>. I respond within 30 days.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>7. Cookies and tracking</h2>
      <p>
        This website <strong>does not use tracking cookies, analytics, or advertising systems</strong>.
        Only technical <code>localStorage</code> values needed for the interface to work properly
        (e.g. cursor preference, hero variant selection during development) are stored in your
        browser. These never leave your browser and are not transmitted to any server.
      </p>
      <p>If I add an analytics tool in the future, I'll update this document and add a cookie consent banner if needed.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>8. Updates to this document</h2>
      <p>
        I may update this document if legislation or processing scope changes. The current
        version is always published at this URL with the last-updated date at the top.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 56px 120px;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .legal section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .legal p {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .legal ul {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .legal li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .legal a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .legal-meta {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .legal-meta li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--ink) 12%, transparent);
  }
  .legal-meta li:first-child {
    border-top: 0;
  }
  .legal-meta span {
    opacity: 0.55;
    min-width: 140px;
  }
  .placeholder {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 22%, transparent);
    color: var(--accent3, var(--ink));
    padding: 1px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ink) 7%, transparent);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .legal { padding: 56px 32px 100px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal {
      padding: 40px 20px 80px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .legal h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .legal { padding: 32px 16px 64px; font-size: 15px; }
    .legal h2 { font-size: 20px; }
  }
</style>
